  <brief_title>Spirometry in Mechanically Ventilated Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Spirometry in Mechanically Ventilated COPD Patients: Correlation of Lung Function Tests to Successful Weaning From Mechanical Ventilation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
